%E9%A6%99%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E5%8F%B7%E4%B8%A4%E5%B2%81%E4%BA%86%23">#丁香医生机构号两岁了#</a> <br><a class="member_mention" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/b4854b0ef6dcd22ce978860a19066e73" data-hash="b4854b0ef6dcd22ce978860a19066e73" data-hovercard="p$b$b4854b0ef6dcd22ce978860a19066e73">@丁香医生</a>  知乎机构号两岁生快！ <a class="member_mention" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/de3d495ab7d3324defc44f11386eccdb" data-hash="de3d495ab7d3324defc44f11386eccdb" data-hovercard="p$b$de3d495ab7d3324defc44f11386eccdb">@丁香妈妈</a> 一周年生快！ <br><br>抽奖快讯：<br>为庆祝双喜，感谢知友的陪伴，丁香医生团队决定来一次小抽奖活动，奖品都是团队内部的周边（奖项设置和奖品见图~~）<br><br>参与方法：<br>从现在起到明天（10月19日）午夜零点之前，转发 @丁香医生 最近的那条想法，说出你的健康疑惑，就可以参与活动啦。获奖名单将会在下周公布，届时丁香医生会和中奖的 30 名知友私信沟通，为你们寄出奖品。 快来拉低中奖率吧~ </span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-more Button--plain">阅读全文<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div><div><div class="RichText ztext PinItem-remainContentRichText"><div class="Image-Wrapper-Preview"><div class="Thumbnail-Wrapper" style="width:;height:"><span class="Image-PreviewVague"><div class="VagueImage Image-Preview" data-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-54caeb097e5273d202e259009ed37bfc_xl.jpg"><div class="VagueImage-mask is-active"></div></div></span></div><div class="Thumbnail-Wrapper" style="width:;height:"><span class="Image-PreviewVague"><div class="VagueImage Image-Preview" data-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-921463aa3bba20bb027fe4a45b0e8e4d_xl.jpg"><div class="VagueImage-mask is-active"></div></div></span></div><div class="Thumbnail-Wrapper" style="width:;height:"><span class="Image-PreviewVague"><div class="VagueImage Image-Preview" data-src="https://pic1.z